        "TileImage": "$($repository 335ce4e7-36bb-45cd-aa24-18564d48ed4e).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47. today you have been issued a contract to eliminate the Sheikh and his personal body guard Michel charest. You will also need to eliminate his good friend Benoit Lagarde. you might wonder why there so important. well they are all accociated with IAGO&apos;s crime deal with the money man, Victor Novikov. This deal is supposed to be secret but for us, its well known, take them out, without arrousing suspision and the money shall be issued to you account, good luck 47.",
